parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the multi-switch assembly can cause various electrical systems to malfunction, including turn signals, horn, electrical windshield, and cruise control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: No response from turn signals
horn
electrical windshield
or cruise control; intermittent or complete failure of these systems; engine stalling while in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Switch Failure Leading to Engine Stalling
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the switches can cause the engine to stall while in motion, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine stalling while in motion; loss of power to various electrical systems; inability to start the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Response from BMW NA
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of response from BMW NA to address the issue of faulty multi-switch assemblies can lead to a sense of frustration and mistrust among customers, potentially affecting their safety and satisfaction.
symptoms: Unresponsive or unhelpful customer service; lack of recall or reimbursement for faulty parts; feeling of being ignored or dismissed by the manufacturer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, engine misfires, and potentially serious injuries or accidents.
symptoms: Fuel odor
fuel leaks
wetness on clothing or surfaces
engine misfires
engine stalling
and potential fires.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the center stand can cause the motorcycle to fall, resulting in damage to the vehicle and potential injury to the rider or bystanders.
symptoms: The center stand bends or collapses while trying to stand up the motorcycle
making it difficult or impossible to use the stand.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Fluid Foaming in Front Reservoir
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Foaming brake fluid in the front reservoir can lead to brake failure, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Brake fluid in the front reservoir is foaming
indicating a potential brake system failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rear brake lockup can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The rear brakes lock up
making it difficult or impossible to move the vehicle
even when the clutch lever is pulled and the vehicle is in neutral.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause a serious safety hazard, especially when riding at high speeds, as it can lead to loss of control, accidents, or leave the rider stranded.
symptoms: The engine dies or stalls without warning
occurs at idle or various speeds up to 50 mph
happens with the clutch in or out
in gear or neutral
and can occur with one or two riders.
